## 9. Update the Frontend for Mainnet

### Step 9.1: Update constants.ts

You already did this in Step 7.1, but double-check that every single address is correct:

- `PROGRAM_ID` → Your mainnet Program ID from Step 6
- `CARDANO_MINT` → `2HE1yvnVitiBEzU1fud7kPsGv89eP7TBwSd8D3tPpump`
- `SSS10i_MINT` → From Step 2
- `LP_MINT` → From Step 4 (first pool's LP)
- `NFT_MINT` → From Step 5
- `USDC_MINT` → Use real mainnet USDC: `EPjFWdd5AufqSSqeM2qN1xzybapC8G4wEGGkZwyTDt1v`
- `TARGET_POOL_PUBKEY` → From Step 7.7 (your first pool pubkey)

### Step 9.2: Update mockApi.ts Pool Definitions

Open `src/utils/mockApi.ts`. Each pool object has an `lpMintAddress` and `poolPubkey`. Update them:

```typescript
{
    id: "pool-1",
    title: "ABG Factory",
    subtitle: "CARDANO / SOL",
    // ...
    lpMintAddress: "YOUR_CARDANO_SOL_LP_MINT_ADDRESS",
    poolPubkey: "YOUR_POOL_1_PUBKEY_FROM_STEP_7"
},
{
    id: "pool-2",
    title: "Stable Ice",
    subtitle: "CARDANO / USDC",
    // ...
    lpMintAddress: "YOUR_CARDANO_USDC_LP_MINT_ADDRESS",
    poolPubkey: "YOUR_POOL_2_PUBKEY_FROM_STEP_7"
},
// ... repeat for all 6 pools
```

### Step 9.3: Remove DevDebug From Production

Open `src/App.tsx`:

1. Delete the import line at the top:

```diff
- import DevDebug from './components/DevDebug';
```

2. Delete the component at the bottom of the JSX (near the footer):

```diff
- <DevDebug />
```

### Step 9.4: Update the IDL Program ID

Open `src/idl/site_zero_matrix.ts`. Scroll to the very bottom and find:

```typescript
programId: "68BXyaV2EfZxMGCo24uDnMGze4HrUozLDomvfS8CrjzF";
```

Replace it with your new mainnet Program ID if it changed.

---

## 10. Build and Deploy the Frontend

### Step 10.1: Build the Production Bundle

```bash
cd ./
npm run build
```

This creates a `dist/` folder with optimized HTML, CSS, and JS.

### Step 10.2: Deploy to Your Hosting Provider

#### Vercel (Recommended — Free)

1. Go to [https://vercel.com](https://vercel.com) and sign in with GitHub.
2. Click **Add New** → **Project**.
3. Import your Git repository or drag-and-drop the `dist/` folder.
4. Set **Framework Preset** to `Vite`.
5. Click **Deploy**.
6. Your site will be live at `https://your-project.vercel.app`.

#### Cloudflare Pages (Also Free)

1. Go to [https://dash.cloudflare.com](https://dash.cloudflare.com) → **Pages**.
2. Click **Create a project** → **Direct upload**.
3. Drag the entire `dist/` folder into the upload area.
4. Click **Deploy**.

#### Manual Upload (Any Web Host)

1. Upload the contents of the `dist/` folder to your web server's public directory.
2. Make sure `index.html` is served as the root page.

### Step 10.3: Point Your Domain

If you want it on a custom domain (e.g., `defi.sss10i.com`):

1. In your hosting provider (Vercel/Cloudflare), go to **Settings** → **Domains**.
2. Add `defi.sss10i.com`.
3. In your domain registrar's DNS settings, add a CNAME record pointing to your hosting provider.

---

## 11. Post-Launch Testing Checklist

Once the site is live, run through this checklist with a real mainnet wallet:

- [ ] **Connect Wallet:** Click "Select Wallet" and connect via Phantom on both desktop and mobile.
- [ ] **View Pools:** All 6 pools should display correct names, icons, and stats.
- [ ] **Enable Container:** Click "Enable Container" on any pool. A Solana transaction should appear. Approve it.
- [ ] **Deposit LP:** Enter an amount and click "Deposit". Approve the transaction. Your staked balance should update.
- [ ] **Verify Reward Accumulation:** Wait 2–3 minutes. The "SSS10i Earned" value should slowly increase from `0.000` to a very small decimal.
- [ ] **Harvest:** Click "Harvest". Approve the transaction. Your Phantom wallet's SSS10i balance should increase.
- [ ] **Withdraw:** Enter an amount and click "Withdraw". Approve. Your LP tokens return to your wallet.
- [ ] **Wrap (NFT → Fractions):** Go to the Wrap tab. If you own an NFT from the collection, test wrapping it.
- [ ] **Unwrap (Fractions → NFT):** If you have enough fractions, test unwrapping back to an NFT.
- [ ] **DEX Swap:** Go to the DEX tab. Try a small swap (e.g., 0.001 SOL → SSS10i).
- [ ] **Mobile Test:** Open the site on your phone's Phantom browser. Verify the bottom tab bar, wallet connectivity, and all interactions work.

---

