## Rollback Plan

If something goes wrong after deploying:

1. **Frontend:** Re-deploy the previous `dist/` folder from your Git history.
2. **Smart Contract:** The authority wallet (your wallet) can call `update_emission_rate` to set reward rate to `0`, effectively pausing all emissions. Users can still withdraw their LP tokens.
3. **Treasury:** If rewards are too high, call the "FIX (LOWER) REWARD RATE" button from DevDebug to lower the emission velocity.
